metadata.name: C–00001 ↼⇀ Cuba, 1980
metadata.description:
With the Moon hanging over humanity's head for as long the species has been in existence, with the rise of space shuttles from a bit player to a space behemoth, with the prevailing social system on Earth as some sort of state capitalism, one source of the complexity is the varying understanding of "culture".

Properties:

4K, 3840x3840, mp4
AAC, Stereo

Utilities:

Our HCPM gives to the collectors of our modules the opportunity to get benefits from the STAMPBODEGA brand as well as they could influence on the different campaigns and collaborations between our brand and another companies which we will announce in the near future. 

For now, first collector buying our NFT's will get:

- t–shirt;
- stickers;
- high resolution printed poster;
- actual physical stamp, which used in this module.

Notice, that physical objects will ship to the owners of NFT, as soon as we will contact the collector.
